{"TopicId":221410,"ForumId":208,"TopicTitle":"G-Meter does not show negative values.","CreatedByName":"DaveLChgo","CreatedById":179012,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T04:26:25Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"DaveLChgo","CreatedById":179012,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T04:26:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Win 11 build 22621.2861 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A012 Gen i7 12700 2.10 GHz | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVidia GeForce RTX 3060 Ti 8GB | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32 GB DDR5 RAM\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIssue:\u003Cbr\u003E\nG-Meter does not show negative values.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSetup:\u003Cbr\u003E\nAny aircraft flying level.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCondition:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nPull back on stick and plane climbs.\u00A0 G-Meter increases positive values as well.\u00A0 This is expected behavior.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nPush forward on stick and plane descends.\u00A0 G-Meter increases positive values again.\u00A0 \u00A0This is unexpected behavior.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDesired Result:\u003Cbr\u003E\nG-Meter should drop to negative values (below the green bar) when pushing forward on the stick.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cvideo class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 controls=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.global.core.embeddedvideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Csource type=\u0022video/mp4\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2023_12/GMeterTest.mp4.c9c49424890de5414fe9e5b4c46e1313.mp4\u0022\u003E\u003Ca class=\u0022ipsAttachLink\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/attachment.php?id=1155\u0026amp;key=8ef4a9cb9ad9941af1c88fccdbda1da6\u0022 data-fileid=\u00221155\u0022 data-fileext=\u0022mp4\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EGMeterTest.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/video\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=GoliathAircraft.zip\u0026amp;fileKey=%5B!AES128GCM%5BoOL20aTM5HkTdZ%2BJ6Xn%2BAfxaAUYSNRRToiQILMb1vrWGMcJ9H26HsTfDq4nGXK14K2al6t%2BzIdnaA5oClAjq5nnTkEY=%5D%5Bfa26567a0976e8c9f24a405e%5D%5Bbf1fdf1e4105b5f74cba1933ab510430%5D%5D\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EGoliathAircraft.zip\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-20T13:52:29Z\u0022 title=\u002212/20/2023 01:52  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 20\u0022\u003EDecember 20, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by The Space Peacock\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}